    "original_title": "Once a Man’s World, Now a Shared Space: Women Transform Mogadishu’s Fish Market.",
    "slug": "women-gain-ground-in-mogadishu-s-traditionally-male-dominated-fish-market",
    "summary": "The Hamar Weyne Fish Market in Mogadishu, long run by men, now sees increasing female participation as the Kaahiye Women’s Fisheries Cooperative helps over 150 women build livelihoods in the fishing sector.",
    "content": "In Mogadishu, the Hamar Weyne Fish Market has historically been a male-dominated space where fishermen and traders conducted business from dawn. However, a notable shift is underway as women increasingly take on roles as vendors and entrepreneurs in the market. The Kaahiye Women’s Fisheries Cooperative, comprising over 150 members, has been instrumental in this change, providing women with the support needed to enter a field that was once considered off-limits to them.\n\nThe cooperative allows women to pool resources, share knowledge, and access fish supplies directly from fishermen, reducing reliance on middlemen. Members sell fresh fish to local customers, earning income that supports their families. This economic activity is particularly significant in a city where employment opportunities for women remain limited.\n\nFor the Somali diaspora, this development underscores the evolving economic landscape in Mogadishu and the potential for women-led initiatives to drive change. It reflects broader societal shifts towards gender inclusion in public and commercial life, offering a model for similar efforts in other sectors.\n\nThe growth of women's participation in the fish market also highlights the importance of cooperative structures in overcoming barriers to entry. By working collectively, these women have managed to carve out a sustainable niche in an industry that previously excluded them.\n\nRead the original report from Radio Dalsan here: https://radiodalsan.com/2026/07/18/once-a-mans-world-now-a-shared-space-women-transform-mogadishus-fish-market/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=once-a-mans-world-now-a-shared-space-women-transform-mogadishus-fish-market",
